Body: Description: CAP is not working as expected. I'm uploading a test spreadsheet with hundreds of fake SSN numbers to dlptest.com and its not appearing in the CAP logs. This used to work fine, and no changes were recently made to the CAP policies.

What We've Learned Updated: the customer is saying that the policies do trigger correctly for SSN numbers.
